cbf1aedf5e30b95b393529753aee30ee:
mutation updateMyUserProfileMutation(
  $input: UpdateMyProfileInput!
) {
  updateMyUserProfile(input: $input) {
    me {
      email
      name
      phone
      profession
      otherRelevantPositions
      bio
      icon {
        internalID
        imageURL
      }
      location {
        display
        city
        state
        country
        id
      }
      lengthUnitPreference
      currencyPreference
      receiveLotOpeningSoonNotification
      receiveNewSalesNotification
      receiveNewWorksNotification
      receiveOutbidNotification
      receivePromotionNotification
      receivePurchaseNotification
      receiveSaleOpeningClosingNotification
      priceRangeMin
      priceRangeMax
      priceRange
      id
    }
  }
}
ce53ad9a1a3f1d1e256af1d6117f4d53:
query SearchCriteriaQuery(
  $alertId: String!
) {
  me {
    email
    alert(id: $alertId) {
      acquireable
      additionalGeneIDs
      atAuction
      attributionClass
      colors
      dimensionRange
      height
      inquireableOnly
      locationCities
      majorPeriods
      materialsTerms
      offerable
      partnerIDs
      priceRange
      width
      sizes
      id
    }
    id
  }
}
eaa237911a19c5c76a5bca49f994e70a:
query SavedSearchAlertQuery(
  $alertId: String!
) {
  me {
    alert(id: $alertId) {
      acquireable
      additionalGeneIDs
      artistIDs
      artistSeriesIDs
      atAuction
      attributionClass
      colors
      dimensionRange
      displayName
      sizes
      height
      inquireableOnly
      locationCities
      majorPeriods
      materialsTerms
      offerable
      partnerIDs
      priceRange
      settings {
        email
        name
        push
        details
      }
      width
      id
    }
    id
  }
}
